text: Su-24 Fencer is a Russian supersonic attack aircraft. In 1974, it came into service in the Soviet Union. It has variable-sweep wing. It has two engines. It has two seats. It is still active in Russian Air Force. Some other countries have also this airplane. This fighter is active in these countries: Russia, Ukraine, Iran, Algeria, Kazakhstan, Syria, Azerbaijan.
